description: Application for approval of reserved matters being scale, appearance, landscaping and layout for Phase One to provide 117 residential units (76 houses and 41 apartments) and A1/ D1 floorspace following the outline application 15/00370/OUTM for the re-development of the former Linpac site comprising of up to 336 residential units in a mix of one, two, three and four bed houses and flats, up to 500 sq.m. of flexible A1/ D1 floorspace, public open space (including childrens playspace), associated landscaping and car parking.
